summary: Adds Imagespace Modifiers to be applied in-game.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a collection of Imagespace Modifiers, which can be applied through the console command:

\"Applyimagespacemodifier modifiernamehere\".

To remove an Imagespace Modifier:

\"Removeimagespacemodifier modifiernamehere\"

List of Imagespace Modifiers added:

AAAFyTy001 - Increases saturation and a few other things to add a more fantastical feel to Skyrim.

AAAFyTy002 - Overlays an orange colour over the screen. Adds a different atmosphere when used with 001.

AAAFyTyBloomThresholdMinus - Increases the \'radius\' of bloom.

AAAFyTyBloomThresholdPlus - Decreases the \'radius\' of bloom.

AAAFyTyMinusBlur - Decreases strength of DOF
author: FiftyTifty
